title: War of the Roses: She's a New York Jets Cheerleader
description: Sydney's brother Scott has been single for a very long time and now suddenly is claiming that he's dating a NY Jets cheerleader.  Sydney has asked to see pictures of the two of them together but he said he doesn't have any.  Scott came home for Christmas and didn't bring her so Sydney is just wondering if Scott is actually dating a professional cheerleader or if he's making it up.
